        "associatedWithLink": "https://www.linkedin.com/company/1646/",
        "description": "Control Google Maps with your hand and a webcam!\nThis was my final project for CS283: Computer Vision (Fall 2012).\n\nGithub: https://github.com/kennyyu/cs283-project\nDemo: http://www.youtube.com/watch?v=DFPg-9D46kE\nWriteup: https://github.com/kennyyu/cs283-project/blob/master/writeup/yu-writeup.pdf\n\nThe goal of this project is to improve hand tracking accuracy, given a poorly trained Haar Cascade Classifier (250 positive samples and 100 negative samples) to recognize hands. To do this, I built a pipeline of several stages to improve the quality of the tracking. In addition, I built a sample web app using this hand tracking pipeline to control Google Maps using your hand and a webcam.\n\n",
